com.ibm.team.repository.common.query.ast
Interface IFilterElement

All Known Subinterfaces:
IBoolean, IBooleanField, IBooleanInputArg, IBooleanLiteral, IDateTime, IDateTimeField, IDateTimeInputArg, IDateTimeLiteral, IEnum, IEnumField, IEnumInputArg, IEnumLiteral, IField, IInputArg, IItemHandleInputArg, IItemTypeInputArg, ILiteral, INumeric, INumericField, INumericInputArg, INumericLiteral, INumericScalarFunction, IScalarFunction, IString, IStringField, IStringInputArg, IStringLiteral, IStringScalarFunction, IUUID, IUUIDField, IUUIDInputArg, IUUIDLiteral
public interface IFilterElement

Filter elements are query elements that can be used as operands of an IPredicate. For example, instances of IField are valid for comparison while instances of IAggregateFunction are not.

Since:
0.5
See Also:
IQuery, IItemQuery, IDataQuery
